      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 20:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和马斯克在投票前权衡参议院领袖之争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/donald-trump-says-senate-s-next-leader-must-favor-recess-appointments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普和埃隆·马斯克向下一任参议院共和党领袖提出要求，这可能会打乱原本预计由米奇·麦康奈尔的长期盟友之一赢得的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/donald-trump-says-senate-s-next-leader-must-favor-recess-appointments</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 20:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
